  "title": "Accounts Receivable cum Admin Assistant (Redhill, SAP)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage accounts receivable tasks including receipt processing, invoicing, statements, credit control, and intercompany billing.</li><li>Assist with GST computation, corporate tax schedules, and verification of employee claims.</li><li>Liaise with freight forwarders on vendor verification and resolve billing discrepancies.</li><li>Provide administrative support covering office supplies, courier coordination, and IT liaison.</li><li>Assist with GST computation, corporate tax schedules, and verification of employee claims.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma in Accountancy, Finance or equivalent</li><li>At least 2 years of accounts and admin experience.</li><li>Strong numerical accuracy, attention to detail, and ability to handle confidential information.</li><li>Proficient in <strong>Microsoft Excel </strong>and <strong>SAP system.</strong></li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
